@startuml

|Lead|
start
:Clicks the "Edit" button in one Project Goals;
|System|
:Makes modifiable the inputs of the Project Goal;
if(Did the User click the "Cancel" button?) is (yes) then
    stop
else(no)
end if

|Lead|
:Modifies any input;
:Clicks a button;

|System|
if(Did the User click the "Save" button?) is (yes) then
else(no)
    stop
    note right
        Go back to Did the User click the "Close" button?
    end note
end if

|System|
if(Is the title input empty?) is (yes) then
    |System|
    :“Save” button gets disabled;
    |Lead|
    :Shows the message “Some obligatory fields are empty”;
    stop
    note right
        Go to User types the title
    end note
    |System|

else(no)
    |System|
    :Compared the project goal's titles with input title;
    if(Is the goal title repeated in the current project?) is (yes) then
        |System|
        :“Save” button gets disabled;
        |Lead|
        :Shows the message “Repeated title, type a new one”;
        stop
        note right
            Go to User types the title
        end note
        |System|
    else(no)
        if(Is the description input empty?) is (yes) then
            |System|
            :“Save” button gets disabled;
            |Lead|
            :Shows the message “Some obligatory fields are empty”;
            stop
            note right
                Go to User types the description
            end note
            |System|
        else(no)
        end if

        if(Is the goal status empty?) is (yes) then
            |System|
            :“Save” button gets disabled;
            |Lead|
            :Shows the message “Some obligatory fields are empty”;
            stop
            note right
                Go to User selects status 
            end note
            |System|
        else(no)
    end if
end if
    |System|
    :Accepts the Lead input;
    :Sends modifications to the Goal project;
    |Database|
    :Modifies the Goal object;
    |System|
    :Gathers modified Goal information through query;
    |Database|
    :Returns queries response;
